&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Are you a registered nurse that enjoys a challenge? If so then we want to hear from you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;An exciting opportunity as arisen for a Full Time, Band 7 Adult Joint Funding , PHB and Transitions Nurse to join our team. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Working within the Continuing HealthCare Team  in BNSSG, you will be based at South Plaza ( Working from Home currently) , though as the post holder you will be expected to travel to different sites and may spend some part of your time working from home&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; The post holder will support the Head of Adult Funded CHC Operations and the Head of Complex Care in ensuring the people of Bristol, North Somerset and South Gloucestershire (BNSSG) experience the best possible quality of services, clinical outcomes and patient experience when they interface with health and care providers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
